    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(C) In nomine domini Dei aeterni <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/21">Berengarius </persName><rs key="#Emperor/king"
                        >rex</rs>. Si predecessorum nostrorum morem imitamur et fidelium
                        petitionibus assensum prebemus, et devotiores illos in nostrae fidelitatis
                        obsequium reddimus. Proinde cunctorum fidelium sanctae Dei Ecclesiae
                        nostrorumque presentium ac futurorum sollicitudo comperiat, quoniam
                            <persName key="#Vir_inluster #fidelisOf" ref="#people/188">Grimaldus
                            </persName><rs key="#Vir_inluster">illustris vir</rs> ac <rs
                            key="#fidelisOf">devotus fidelis </rs>noster suppliciter nostrae
                        serenitatis clementiam adiit petens, ut cuidam <rs key="#fidelisOf">fideli
                            nostro</rs> nomine <persName key="#fidelisOf">Teudiberto</persName>
                        <placeName ref="#places/306" key="#Other_administrative_unit"><rs
                                key="#Other_administrative_unit">vallem
                            Prujvinianum</rs></placeName> habitatori, in <rs key="#Villas">villa
                        </rs>videlicet eiusdem vallis que nominatur <placeName key="#Villas"
                            ref="#places/307">Canciagum</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >vineas</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >terram arabilem</rs> in duobus locis ubi nuncupatur <placeName
                            key="#Mountains #Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >ad Titulum</placeName>, nec non et <placeName
                            key="#Mountains #Landed_possessions #Wine #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >Fasenariam </placeName>ex integro cum <rs
                            key="#Mountains #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >montibus</rs> atque <rs>planiciebus</rs>, seu et quandam <rs
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >silvam</rs> quae <geogName
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Fines"
                                ><placeName
                                key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Fines"
                                ref="#places/308">Lamola vocitatur, et Panicum </placeName>cum <rs
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Fines"
                                >omnibus finibus</rs></geogName> suis in integrum, prout dudum
                            <geogName key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/124">ad <rs key="#Comitatus"
                                >comitatum</rs> Veronensem</geogName> respiciebant, pro [Dei a]more
                        et remedio animae nostrae sive pro eiusdem Teudiberti <rs key="#gratitudeTo"
                            >sedulo servitio</rs> per hoc nostrae auctoritatis preceptum concedere
                        dignaremur. Cuius dignis petitionibus nostrae serenitatis aures
                        accomodantes, prenominatas vineas et terram arabilem in duobus locis ubi ad
                        Titulum dicitur, seu et Fasenariam cum totis suis confinibus videlicet cum
                        montibus et planiciebus, nec non et silvam quam Lamulam dicunt, nec non et
                        Panicum sub integritate prefato Teudiberto iure proprietario, sicut dudum
                        regie parti pertinuerunt, superius comprehensa perhenniter hac nostrae
                        auctoritatis pagina concedimus et largimur, ac de nostro iure dominioque in
                        suum ius atque dominium omnino transfundimus et donamus, ut habeat, teneat,
                        possideat, commutet, venundetur, pro anima iudicet faciatque in omnibus et
                        per omnia quicquid suus decreverit animus vel voluntas, omni potestate vel
                        contradictione remota. Si quis igitur hoc nostrae auctoritatis preceptum
                        infringere temptaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi
                            libras centum</rs>, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere palatii
                            nostri </rs>et medietatem prefato Teudiberto <rs key="#heirTo">suisque
                            heredibus</rs>. Quod ut verius credatur et diligentius observetur, manu
                        propria roborantes de anulo nostro subter insigniri precepimus. Signum domni
                        (MF) Berengarii serenissimi regis. <persName key="#Chancellor"
                            >Ambrosius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> ad vicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/216">Ardingi </persName><rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopi </rs>et <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarli </rs>recognovi et subscripsi. (SR) (SI n. n) Data
                        .VII. kal. iun., anno dominicae incarnationis .DCCCV., domni Vero Berengarii
                        invictissimi regis .XVIII., indictione .VIII. Actum <orgName
                            key="#Plebs #Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/121"><placeName
                                key="#Plebs #Churches" ref="#places/306">valle Pruviniano iuxta <rs
                                    key="#Plebs #Churches">plebem</rs> Sancti
                            Floriani</placeName></orgName>. feliciter, amen. </ab>
                </div>
